trikz_legends by Keke. & Gaaamer.

Map contains:

14 Lvls + 2 secrets
3 Bonuslvls + RB-Bonus (532-548)

The map should be much bigger, but due some bugs and because our collabs partner left the collaberation, we decided to upload it as it is. That is why the map doesnt contain skyjump and totem...

Anyway...have fun playing it, even though it is short.
